name: A girl ...
description: A girl was born during pandemic. Nowadays, many people have been wearing face mask when they are going out every day. There have a lot of problem in her county and the girl want to speak out about her position and opinion. Unfortunately, she can’t speak because she is still wearing face mask. So what’s under her mask? and what do you think about this picture?  You will get jpg file size 6000x6000.
